stages.name: WALD
stages.description: Get ready to hit the Wald floor! This is the place to be if you love hard, driving techno beats that will get you dancing all night long. With a straight-forward, energetic vibe, this spot is perfect for those who crave the heavier, more energetic sounds. The light setup is next level, creating a super cool atmosphere, and the laser show will blow your mind and elevate your dance experience to the next level.

stages.name: WIESE
stages.description: Check out the Wiese house music floor! It’s the perfect place to kick back and enjoy some smooth, soulful beats. The vibe is super chill and friendly, with great melodies and deep bass that’ll keep you grooving all night. This is the place to really immerse yourself in the warm, soulful sounds of House music, for good vibes and good times.

stages.name: BUK CORNER
stages.description: Nestled among birch and beech trees by the lake, this forest stage pulses with deep house, minimal, and hypnotic grooves. From underground legends to rising talents, the lineup promises immersive journeys and late-night magic. A place to dance, drift, and lose yourself in sound and nature.

stages.name: SEE
stages.description: See floor is the village square of Garbicz Festival. And its rule is: Everything is allowed! Everything must be! Start the afternoon with an onstage cooking show, carefully curated music or folkloric concerts, or enjoy cabaret and drag performances in the evening. This goes all the way to mindless niche raving through the night.

SATURDAY.artist: Rico Loop feat. The Pappenheimer's live

stages.name: LOCO PARAISO
stages.description: Welcome to a crazy paradise that blends Mexico’s vibrant soul with Berlin’s creative chaos in the depths of the Polish forest. Join us for a four-day burst of sonic, sabor, and soul. And expect nothing less than godly tacos, psychedelic grooves, and surreal magic – all powered by Wrocław’s Sound Experience crew.

SUNDAY.artist: b2b: O.BEE - Tomas Station - Triana - Rakim

stages.name: AMBIENT FLOOR
stages.description: Lila Collective delivers a multidimensional sanctuary of deep listening, ambient textures, and sensory immersion – blending world music, organic-electronic soundscapes, live acts, sunrise rituals, video installations, scent, and tea bar in a dreamlike, living stage experience.

stages.name: JUICY
stages.description: What to say? It’s a ‘if you know, you know’ thing… It began as a humble juice hut that morphed into a wild dance floor, attracting global misfits alike. Our suggestion: hit the floor, and see it with your own eyes. Then you’ll know too. It‘s hard to explain, but real easy to love.

SATURDAY.artist: WLC presents The Wezienwel Ensemble ft JO.KE

stages.name: PLEASURE ISLAND
stages.description: Welcome to Pleasure Island. Where Afro meets Trance, and tooth gems sparkle up your smile while dancing next to the lake. Between disco and desire, performance and play, this is where softness is a superpower and the bold, and the sexy come alive. It‘s not a stage – it‘s a space to be seen, to transform, to let go.

stages.name: LICHTUNG
stages.description: Step into your sanctuary of human connection and playful wonders. Drift between workshops, performances, and healing sounds, or enjoy massages & bodywork. Find clarity in the Sober Space. Feel the vibrations of the Soundtube. Relax, recharge, and reconnect with yourself, nature, and all the colorful unicorns around you.

THURSDAY.artist: Velvet Whispers by Zohar feat. Ha:arp

stages.name: WEINBAR
stages.description: The Garbicz cult classic just got reinvented. And that means: more wine, more bubbles. A better, even more fun program including vinyl DJs and karaoke. Even a Champagne tasting! Let‘s get winy.
